comment: Lemma for ~ hsmex . Bound the order type of a union of sets of ordinals, each of limited order type. Vaguely reminiscent of ~ unictb but use of order types allows to canonically choose the sub-bijections, removing the choice requirement. (Contributed by Stefan O'Rear, 14-Feb-2015.) (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 26-Jun-2015.) (Revised by AV, 18-Sep-2021.)
